"Gs" is an abbreviation and can have different meanings depending on the context. Here are some possible translations:

- Gramm-Sekunde (unit of force)
- Gauß (unit of magnetic flux density)
- Gravitationseinheit (unit of gravitational acceleration)
- Geländesport (outdoor sports)
- Geschwindigkeitsänderung (change in velocity)
- Gleichstrom (direct current)
- Gas-Schweißen (gas welding)
